author: akarasulu
msg: Fixed the problem reported by David Geleyn where disabling anonymous binds was
not taking effect.  Turns out to avoid a dep on the apacheds core in the ldap
protocol provider we did not use EnvKeys.DISABLE_ANONYMOUS but used the property
string.  The property key was eve.disable.anonymous but was changed in EnvKeys
to server.disable.anonymous.  So the feature stopped working.
